metadata.name: OceanVerse #1/3
metadata.description:
1/1

This is the first item on my Foundation app journey and i wish that it brings to me a good fortune. 

The collection items captured maiden parts of the world oceans, thanks to my job. 

This piece from Mid Pacific Ocean, it was a quite stormy day, I captured couple of wave photos and transformed with digital art into this. there are 2 more variation of this item, which i planned to mint next. 

I hope you'll like my artworks and support me on this cause I have a huge collection to show and feed you :) 

Thanks and best regards.
